OL,3,CHow much will your water provider
OL,4,Craise its bills by?
OL,6,FWater bills are set to climb by an
OL,7,Faverage of #157 over the next five
OL,8,Fyears, the industry regulator has
OL,9,Fconfirmed.
OL,11,FOfwat's figures have angered consumer
OL,12,Fgroups, who have criticised many water
OL,13,Ffirms' records on sewage spills and
OL,14,Fwater leaks.
OL,16,FThe amount bills are going up by
OL,17,Fdiffers depending on each individual
OL,18,Fwater company. But how has this
OL,19,Fhappened - and how much more will
OL,20,Fpeople have to pay?
