OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FWhy are water bills increasing?
OL,13,FWater firms in England and Wales
OL,14,Fsubmit plans to Ofwat every five years
OL,15,Fon how much they will raise water
OL,16,Fbills.
OL,18,FOfwat then negotiates with the
OL,19,Fcompanies over how much bills can go
OL,20,Fup by and sets limits, before
OL,21,Fpublishing its final decision.
