OL,3,CHow much will your water provider
OL,4,Craise its bills by?
OL,6,FFor the next five years, Ofwat has
OL,7,Fgranted an average bills increase of
OL,8,F36%, or #31 a year until 2030. The
OL,9,Fregulator added this was, on average,
OL,10,F#8 lower per year compared to what
OL,11,Fcompanies proposed in their plans.
OL,13,FOfwat said it had made sure bills were
OL,14,F"fair", and not higher than they need
OL,15,Fto be. If companies do not meet their
OL,16,Ftargets they must return money to
OL,17,Fcustomers, it added.
OL,19,FHow much is my provider raising them
OL,20,Fby?
